                    You have 60 seconds! Submit as much answer as you can! Good Luck!
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <a class="buttons" href="/mathgame">
                    <button type="button" id="start">Start</button>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div>
                <a class="buttons" href="/dashboard">
                    <button type="button" id="back">Back</button>
                </a>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>


